title: Watch: VICTON Returns With High-Energy Performance Version Of “Eyez Eyez”
text:
Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
VICTON is back with the dance performance version of their latest single “Eyez Eyez”! 
In the video, the seven members show off their individual colors while giving fans a closer look at the song’s full choreography. Returning to the subway station seen in the original music video , the boys keep it fully synchronized, proving themselves to be a rookie group with dance skills to continue looking out for. 
While VICTON continues to promote the single on various music shows, member Subin has been making headlines after signing on for a new variety program . The singer will join members of MADTOWN, AOA, 9MUSES, and more on the upcoming survival show “Idol Acting Competition – I’m an Actor” (tentative title), beginning on April 11. 
Check out the full performance video for “Eyez Eyez” below!
